  <brief_title>Effects of Repeated Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (rTMS) on the Treatment of Cocaine Addicted Patients</brief_title>
  <acronym>TMSCOCDEPEND</acronym>
  <official_title>Efeitos da Estimulacao Magnetica Transcrania de Repeticao ( EMTr) no Tratamento da Dependencia ao Uso de Cocaina</official_title>
